d to warm-start causal priors across problem instances. The impact extends beyond performance: CausalBranch yields interpretable, evolving models of solver behavior, enabling transfer learning across domains and principled debugging of heuristics. It also establishes a new foundation for algorithmic introspection in combinatorial search.",
